791
00:44:19,115 --> 00:44:22,324
I went to a military academy called...

792
00:44:24,036 --> 00:44:26,119
Well, I won't tell you the name.

793
00:44:26,247 --> 00:44:27,488
I had a terrible time there.

794
00:44:29,792 --> 00:44:33,331
My father sent me
to military school, away from home,

795
00:44:33,462 --> 00:44:36,546
the one he had attended.

796
00:44:36,674 --> 00:44:39,883
It was a cruel and unusual punishment.

797
00:44:42,138 --> 00:44:45,176
The mind of the military has one aim:

798
00:44:45,766 --> 00:44:48,884
To be as mechanical as possible.

799
00:44:49,979 --> 00:44:52,722
To function like a human machine.

800
00:44:54,775 --> 00:44:57,893
Individuality simply did not exist.

801
00:44:59,989 --> 00:45:02,197
I had a lot of loneliness.

802
00:45:04,035 --> 00:45:07,745
I spent most of the time
up in the library

803
00:45:07,872 --> 00:45:12,617
reading the <i>National Geographic</i>
magazine about Tahiti.

804
00:45:13,753 --> 00:45:17,588
