00:51:54,194 --> 00:51:55,901
we're all gonna go on the television

925
00:51:56,030 --> 00:51:57,646
and say what we know,

926
00:51:57,781 --> 00:51:59,488
because the country is ignorant.

927
00:52:04,622 --> 00:52:07,285
I am really moved and motivated

928
00:52:07,416 --> 00:52:10,955
by things that occur that are unjust.

929
00:52:12,630 --> 00:52:16,590
I've always hated
people trampling on other people.

930
00:52:19,762 --> 00:52:21,048
I was in a quandary,

931
00:52:21,263 --> 00:52:23,676
